Interface PlcFieldResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PlcMessage, PlcResponse
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PlcReadResponse, PlcSubscriptionEvent, PlcSubscriptionResponse, PlcWriteResponse

    public interface PlcFieldResponse
extends PlcResponse
    Base type for all response messages sent as response for a prior request from a plc to the plc4x system.
